    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review our democratic system. Consult advice from experts in this field.",
        "additional_details": "I am an ex-Captain in the Merchant Navy. I have stood on the outside looking in for my whole life. I have worked and lived with many different nationalities and religions. We all want the same basic things, security, freedom and hope (a chance to prosper). The government should be working to provide such for all. We have lost our way. The only way back is genuine and honest reform. Of the people, by the people for the people!",
        "background": "It is evident that the majority of the people here in the UK and a number of other democratic countries are not happy with the present system. It needs overhauling to better represent the majority. Consult clinical psychologists, the political think tanks like the RSA and pro-Democracy",
